snippet.title: Looming Walkthrough (All Endings)
snippet.description:
This is a walkthrough of the game "Looming".

Play the game here: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/541333

You can visit my Patreon page if you want or something:
https://www.patreon.com/awalkthroughlife

Game made by GregoryWeir
_____
Game description (from creator):
This game is about two lovers named January and September.
No, wait; it's about a group of people who don't believe in the sky.
No, it's about a pantheon of scientific disciplines.
Or maybe it's about an ancient beast who knew exactly when it was going to die, and how.

It's about a place. A place called Looming.
